                    <span>I bought this book when I was traveling in New Mexico.<br>It is full of spirit and joy!  Read this book!<p>To be a rebel means to be true to your vision.  Chip gives<br>many examples in his book.  Chip is very conscious of how important vision is.  Vision gives your life full-throttle power!!! Chip gives you the tools to craft your<br>vision magnificiently! <p>Read this book, and you will be a rebel in life, wherever you are- New Mexico or Maine or Iowa!  I think this book applies to<br>you whether you running a biz, investing, or thinking about starting a very visionary biz!  Yes!!!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Today you have to be a rebel!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
