                    <span>I have worked for myself for the last nine years and believe that any true rebels would and should through this book out the window.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">entrepreneurial secrets revealed!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
